189&ndash;198.</li>

<li>Harris, George W., 1989a. &lsquo;Integrity and Agent Centered
Restrictions,&rsquo; <em>No&ucirc;s</em>, 23: 437&ndash;456.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1989b. &lsquo;A Paradoxical Departure from
