90&ndash;102.</li>

<li>Hay, Carol, 2012. &lsquo;The Peculiar, the Arbitrary, and the
Different,&rsquo; <em>International Journal of Applied
Philosophy</em>, 28(1): 71&ndash;88.</li>

<li>Hebert, Mark R., 2002. &lsquo;Integrity, Identity and
