<li>Holley, David M., 2002. &lsquo;Self-Interest and Integrity,&rsquo;
<em>International Philosophical Quarterly</em>, 42: 5&ndash;22.</li>

<li>Howard-Snyder, Frances, 1997. &lsquo;The Rejection of Objective
